cscie160.hw3
Class Floor

java.lang.Object
  cscie160.hw3.Floor

public class Floor
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a single Floor among a collection of Floors that is traversed by Elevator. A floor contains three collections of Passengers -- upPassengers, downPassengers, and unqueuedPassengers As well as a floor number

Author:
ryanmitchell
